			It was just me that day and the whole world against me. I planned to buy some books and started looking for deals. I realized very soon that it is almost impossible to know which online shopping site has the best deal for a book, mobile or a camera. That day passed leaving me frustrated. Next day I had a chance discussion with a friend who wanted to buy a DSLR camera. Our tale of frustration tallied and I hatched the plan for - Cheapr.
			</br></br>
