            <h2 class="large-about about-smaller" style="font-size: 26px;">What cheapr is made of or Strictly Geeky Stuff</h2>
            Cheapr is hosted on Ubuntu and uses Nginx with Passenger. 
            Coded mostly in Ruby on Rails, cheapr uses jQuery and is coded mainly in HTML and CSS using Vi. 
            Cheapr uses mongodb, mongoid and memcached for housekeeping and caching. 
            Blazing fast HTTP library 'typhoeus' works well with varnish to get prices from more than 20 online stores in India. 
            There is a lot of heavy lifting happening behind the scenes. Fortunately, you do not need to worry about all this.
